    <briefdescription>
<para>Value type exposed by <ref refid="classDali_1_1ManagedOpenHashMap_1_1Iterator" kindref="compound">Iterator</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides stable references to the key (const) and value (mutable) of a live entry. The key is exposed as const to match std::unordered_map semantics, which prohibits mutating a key through an iterator.</para>
<para>Supports: it-&gt;<ref refid="structDali_1_1ManagedOpenHashMap_1_1KeyValuePair_1a66b1f43207b30d90867911e70d48598e" kindref="member">key()</ref> / it-&gt;<ref refid="structDali_1_1ManagedOpenHashMap_1_1KeyValuePair_1ac50c0743d53a99d68849d78ab2be21ad" kindref="member">value()</ref> — via operator-&gt; on <ref refid="classDali_1_1ManagedOpenHashMap_1_1Iterator" kindref="compound">Iterator</ref> (<emphasis>it).<ref refid="structDali_1_1ManagedOpenHashMap_1_1KeyValuePair_1a66b1f43207b30d90867911e70d48598e" kindref="member">key()</ref> / (*it).<ref refid="structDali_1_1ManagedOpenHashMap_1_1KeyValuePair_1ac50c0743d53a99d68849d78ab2be21ad" kindref="member">value()</ref> — via operator</emphasis> on <ref refid="classDali_1_1ManagedOpenHashMap_1_1Iterator" kindref="compound">Iterator</ref> kv.key() / kv.value() — via range-for: for(auto&amp; kv : map) @SINCE_2_5.20 </para>
    </detaileddescription>
